        <body>
        <div type="letter">
        <opener><dateline><date when="1917-08-04">August 04, 1917.<dateline></date><salute>Dear <persName key="harriet_monroe">Harriet</persName>:</salute>
        </opener>
            <p>Here is the <measure type="currency" num="100">hundred dollars</measure> I promised you for the <date when="1917-09">1st of September</date>.</p>

<!-- added Untermeyer's theseTimes to possible additions -->
            <p>I have got hung up with proof for the moment, but I hope to get my review of <persName>Louis Untermeyer</persName><title key="theseTimes" level="m">’s “These Times”<title> to you before very long.</p>
               <p>That cow-boy song is bully.</p>
                <closer>Affectionately yours,</closer>
            
        </div>    
